description:
This course is designed to give some very practical advice to new and emerging managers and leaders.

  • We will discuss the basics of:
    • Appearance
    • Leading by example
    • Time management
    • Professionalism
    • Communication
    • Serving others.

    This is a 101 class that is quick advice that is practical. You should take this course if you are just starting out in management or if you are thinking about becoming a manager. There are some very basic things that new managers overlook that can hurt your career progress. This course is designed to give you good advice quickly.
title: First Lead Yourself
